title: Survivorman Season 3
description:
The Third and Final Season of Survivorman:

Episode 1: Sierra Nevada
Les plays the role of a backpacker in California's Sierra Nevada mountains and challenges search and rescue teams to find him.
Episode 2: Colorado Rockies
Les survives in Colorado's Rocky Mountains accompanied by two horses.
Episode 3: Artic Tundra
Les goes north to the Arctic Baffin Island equipped as a researcher with some advanced survival gear.
Episode 4: Temagami Hunting (Deep Woods)
Les Stroud is joined by his friend Bob Wilson as they simulate being hunters lost in the forests of Temagami, Ontario.
Episode 5: Australian Outback
After his ultralight airplane runs out of fuel, Les Stroud is stranded in the Australian Outback.
Episode 6: Papua New Guinea
Survivorman Les Stroud is stranded in Papua New Guinea jungle and left to survive alone. Les demonstrates how to start a fire with a butane lighter, suffers from diarrhea, gets high chewing on a betelnut, and films natives singing and dancing in celebration of Les's jungle survival.
